. is going to provide computer lab facilities in 120 ITIs with total outlay of Rs. 10 crore under PPP Model.", "025-listElement": "- Department of Skill Development, Entrepreneurship & Training will provide training to 2.5 lakh people.", "026-listElement": "- Furthermore, govt. is going to extend DISHA Scheme to all districts to provide training to 1 lakh entrepreneurs with total cost of Rs. 2 crore.", "027-listElement": "- **Women** \u2013", "028-listElement": "- Karnataka govt. is going to launch Mukhyamantri Anila Bhagya Yojana to provide free LPG connections to women. Subsequently, this scheme will encourage them towards a smoke free India. Under this scheme, women will get gas connection with 2 Burner Gas Stove and 2 Refill Cylinders absolutely free of cost. The state govt. has allotted Rs. 1350 crore for the successful implementation of this scheme. Accordingly, this scheme will benefit 30 lakh women.", "029-listElement": "- Karnataka govt. is going to provide Incentive of Rs. 3 lakh to SC Boy who marries a girl from other caste. Moreover, govt. will provide Rs. 5 lakh as incentive to an SC Girl for marrying a boy of any other caste.", "030-listElement": "- For women empowerment, govt. will provide Rs. 50,000 loan to the women and fisherman at 0% interest rate.", "031-listElement": "- Furthermore, govt. will provide skill training to women working in IT Sector who are making return after long break / maternity leave.", "032-listElement": "- **Digital Karnataka** \u2013", "033-listElement": "- Karnataka govt. has launched E-Kshana to ease down the process of getting Caste, Residence and Income Certificate online.", "034-listElement": "- Accordingly, govt. has launched Moulya App in order to find the guidance value of any immovable property.", "035-listElement": "- Karnataka govt. will also develop Samyojane App to obtain citizen services of the Department. Furthermore, govt. will also develop Dishank App in order the Survey Number and Map of the spot where a ci